The paper deals with image retrieval, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a convolutional neural network and a U-Net architecture suggests that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The mention of landmarks and datasets such as Oxford and Paris suggests that the paper may also be related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
